  "id": 460830578,
  "question": "如果恐龙没有灭绝，并且没有进化，一直活到现在，那现在这个世界会变成怎样？",
  "author": "山高县",
  "content": "<p>搞不好还是真兽类和虚骨龙类共分天下。</p><p>恐龙时代其实也是竞争激烈的，并不存在永恒的压制，只要有潜力，总是有机会的。</p><p>统治白垩纪晚期和古近纪早期的虚骨龙类，在侏罗纪时混的并不比同时期哺乳类强多少（侏罗纪公园拿虚骨龙类做主角，无异于白垩纪公园拿剑齿虎做主角）。</p><p>如果当时真兽类已经进化成熟的话，虚骨龙能做到的，十有八九也能做到。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d66c773df0d125a301352ef7143951ba_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"651\" data-rawheight=\"392\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e583e462535305edbb428bfc2d26d35f_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"651\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d66c773df0d125a301352ef7143951ba_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;651&#39; height=&#39;392&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"651\" data-rawheight=\"392\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-e583e462535305edbb428bfc2d26d35f_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"651\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d66c773df0d125a301352ef7143951ba_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d66c773df0d125a301352ef7143951ba_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>暴龙的祖宗混的也不怎么样</figcaption></figure><p>虽说白垩纪晚期虚骨龙类和角龙类的崛起，要感谢土伦阶的灭绝事件。但虚骨龙的崛起，主要还是真刀真枪杀出来的。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c014badf234d2fe463fd001b8a349793_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"710\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c5b5dd623f56f81b4767050e84cbb721_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c014badf234d2fe463fd001b8a349793_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;710&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"710\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c5b5dd623f56f81b4767050e84cbb721_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c014badf234d2fe463fd001b8a349793_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c014badf234d2fe463fd001b8a349793_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-69124cce345ef6964011fb7ccc4b4e8b_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"393\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7720b56f0ebe09acef9afbca11a4dae7_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-69124cce345ef6964011fb7ccc4b4e8b_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;393&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"393\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7720b56f0ebe09acef9afbca11a4dae7_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-69124cce345ef6964011fb7ccc4b4e8b_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-69124cce345ef6964011fb7ccc4b4e8b_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5091766a187670d8205336ca4620625e_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"220\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f7963ba65f715b67abda76a79fed3d2a_hd.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"360\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;360&#39; height=&#39;220&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"360\" data-rawheight=\"220\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f7963ba65f715b67abda76a79fed3d2a_hd.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"360\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5091766a187670d8205336ca4620625e_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f0e7dc828a39827b5be97287a8cd5ad2_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"654\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-326059b747ece037b0a6738210ac333a_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f0e7dc828a39827b5be97287a8cd5ad2_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;654&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"654\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-326059b747ece037b0a6738210ac333a_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f0e7dc828a39827b5be97287a8cd5ad2_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f0e7dc828a39827b5be97287a8cd5ad2_hd.jpg\"/></figure><p>哺乳类既然从虚骨龙的后裔手中夺得了天下，那么在虚骨龙大家庭面前分一杯羹，并不是完全不能想象。</p><p>不过有一个很大的变数，就是在兽脚类演化主线，埃雷拉龙——角鼻龙——坚尾龙——肉食龙——虚骨龙——手盗龙这条线上，有一个明显的趋势是前肢越来越灵活。。。。。</p>",
